{"tid":47413,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"用router整network hard-disk","createTime":"2016-12-20T10:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T10:33:26.000Z","uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a05ebe73d04d80e45188bfb801b7363825c8690","tid":47413,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟用梗 Macbook pro ，買咗個外置hard-disk <br />\n但成日插係部嘢到好唔方便，所以就想用router share 個hard-disk 出嚟，係屋企用得舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用梗Asus router ，我插咗hard-disk 入去之後，無論係mac定pc都見唔到部嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都開咗分享硬碟嘅功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激不盡<br />\n<br />\nBetween 部router 只support USB 2.0 而部hard-disk 係用USB 3.0 ，唔知會唔會有關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n有圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返梗屋企"},{"pid":"51f41f561c9dc43512ff84a05f621cf1e5fb10b6","tid":47413,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a850ec80d1a0e6a897e31bf3dc28a2b64e0a21eb","tid":47413,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"用梗ASUS RT-AC51U"},{"pid":"1ab88a987306bbb70d2396b487ccfcaaf2854c9b","tid":47413,"uid":53710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:28:23.000Z","msg":"有關係"},{"pid":"d64f5b22079d90c6762d89371dd32e44193ab6e7","tid":47413,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"即係插個harddisk落router?<br />\n<br />\n依家唔係連落同一個wifi就share到嘢啦咩"},{"pid":"adc2a27ef7bd76e92ec4512e14b7b5247b666f18","tid":47413,"uid":4723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"你自己答左自己啦"},{"pid":"84a379868710cf1cfa6d1a00093e4070f8dcc7bd","tid":47413,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己答左自己啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c94415a8fea9980ed90a40e9e4016b01fc65c85","tid":47413,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"我插仔USB 2.0 手指入去都係用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d095acd70ac50e00fac07b19a992ec21618e71d","tid":47413,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"插入後<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e85Y8Fw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe85Y8Fw.jpg&h=fffae9a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n噤咗之後，出現呢個畫面一下 ，之後就消失<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/20/183324_29618c2de89955ead65d16b576d67cc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F20%2F183324_29618c2de89955ead65d16b576d67cc7.jpg&h=6174de8d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}